 state through its policies on infrastructure, security and youth emancipation.” Vanguard News Mrs. Rashida Bello is the First Lady of Kogi State. In this interview, Rashida speaks on how she has been using her position to impact positively on the people of the state. June 11, 2017 In "Woman's Own" Gov. Yahaya Bello of Kogi State has commended the contributions of the FCT Minister of State, Dr Ramatu Aliyu, to the victory of All Progressives Congress (APC) in 2015 and 2019 general election. October 6, 2019 In "News" THE moves by Kogi first lady, Rashida Bello to bridge the gap in equipment and consumables in Kogi hospitals has given reasons for cheer in the state. The governor's wife has been able to mobilise health equipment worth million of naira for some clinics in the state using her NGO;… April 13, 2017 In "Woman's Own"